[
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"01697 0834 01961 0854 03068\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03414\" class=\"\">Jeremiah</st>:<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "\u201c<st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">Go down</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">at once</st><n id=\"1\" /> to the <st data-num=\"03335\" class=\"\">potter\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st>. I will <st data-num=\"08085 01697\">speak to</st> you further <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st>.\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "So I <st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">went down</st> to the <st data-num=\"03335\" class=\"\">potter\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> and <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">found</st> him <st data-num=\"06213 04399\">working</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">at</st> his <st data-num=\"070\" class=\"\">wheel</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "Now and then<n id=\"1\" /> there would <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">be</st> something <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">wrong</st><n id=\"2\" /> with the <st data-num=\"03627 0834\">pot</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> was <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">molding</st> from the <st data-num=\"02563\" class=\"\">clay</st><n id=\"3\" /> with <st data-num=\"03335\" class=\"\">his</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hands</st>. So he would <st data-num=\"07725 06213\">rework</st><n id=\"4\" /> the clay into <st data-num=\"0312\" class=\"\">another</st> kind of <st data-num=\"03627\" class=\"\">pot</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">as</st> <st data-num=\"03335\" class=\"\">he</st> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">saw</st> <st data-num=\"03474 06213\">fit</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">Then</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me,",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "\u201cI, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">say</st>:<n id=\"1\" /> \u2018O <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">nation</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, <st data-num=\"03201\" class=\"\">can</st> I <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">deal</st> with you as <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"03335\" class=\"\">potter</st> deals with the clay?<n id=\"2\" /> In my <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hands</st>, <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st>, O <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">nation</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, are <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">just</st> <st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">like</st> the <st data-num=\"02563\" class=\"\">clay</st> in this <st data-num=\"03335\" class=\"\">potter\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st>.\u2019 ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "There are <st data-num=\"07281\" class=\"\">times</st>, Jeremiah,<n id=\"1\" /> when I <st data-num=\"01696 05921\">threaten</st> to <st data-num=\"05428\" class=\"\">uproot</st>, <st data-num=\"05422\" class=\"\">tear down</st>, and <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">destroy</st> a <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nation</st> or <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">kingdom</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "But if <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"01471 0834\">nation</st> I <st data-num=\"01696 05921\">threatened</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">stops</st> doing <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">wrong</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> I will <st data-num=\"05162 05921\">cancel</st> the <st data-num=\"07451 0834\">destruction</st><n id=\"2\" /> I <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">intended</st> to <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">do</st> to it.",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "And there are <st data-num=\"07281\" class=\"\">times</st> when I <st data-num=\"01696 05921\">promise</st> to <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">build up</st> and <st data-num=\"05193\" class=\"\">establish</st><n id=\"1\" /> a <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nation</st> or <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">kingdom</st>. ",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "But if that nation <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">does</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">what displeases</st> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">me</st> and does <st data-num=\"01115\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">obey</st> <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">me</st>, then I will <st data-num=\"05162 05921\">cancel</st> the <st data-num=\"02896 0834\">good</st> I <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">promised</st> to <st data-num=\"03190\" class=\"\">do</st> to it.",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st>, <st data-num=\"0559 04994 0413\">tell</st> the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">people</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">and</st> the <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">citizens</st> of <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">this</st>: The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">says</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"02009 0595\">I</st> am <st data-num=\"03335\" class=\"\">preparing</st> to bring <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">disaster</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> you! I am <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">making</st> <st data-num=\"04284\" class=\"\">plans</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to punish</st> you.<n id=\"2\" /> So, <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">every one</st> of you, <st data-num=\"07725 04994\">stop</st> the <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil</st> <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">things</st> you <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">have been doing</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"03190\" class=\"\">Correct</st> the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">way</st> you <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">have been living</st> and <st data-num=\"04611\" class=\"\">do</st> what is right.\u2019<n id=\"4\" />",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "But they just keep <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">saying</st>, \u2018We <st data-num=\"02976\" class=\"\">do not care</st> what you say!<n id=\"1\" /> We will <st data-num=\"0310 01980\">do</st> <st data-num=\"04284\" class=\"\">whatever</st> we <st data-num=\"04284\" class=\"\">want to do</st>! We will continue to <st data-num=\"0376 06213\">behave</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">wickedly</st> and <st data-num=\"08307 03820\">stubbornly</st>!\u2019\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">Therefore</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">says</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"07592 04994\">Ask</st> the people of other <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">whether they</st> have <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> of anything like <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">this</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> should have been like a <st data-num=\"01330\" class=\"\">virgin</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">but she has <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">done</st> <st data-num=\"08186\" class=\"\">something</st> <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">utterly</st> <st data-num=\"08186\" class=\"\">revolting</st>! </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Does the <st data-num=\"07950\" class=\"\">snow</st> ever completely <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">vanish</st> from the <st data-num=\"06697\" class=\"\">rocky</st> slopes of <st data-num=\"03844\" class=\"\">Lebanon</st>?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Do</st> the <st data-num=\"07119\" class=\"\">cool</st> <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">waters</st> from those <st data-num=\"02114\" class=\"\">distant</st> mountains ever <st data-num=\"05203\" class=\"\">cease</st> to <st data-num=\"05140\" class=\"\">flow</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Yet</st> my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> have <st data-num=\"07911\" class=\"\">forgotten</st> me<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"06999\" class=\"\">offered sacrifices</st> to <st data-num=\"07723\" class=\"\">worthless idols</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">This makes them <st data-num=\"03782\" class=\"\">stumble</st> along in the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">way</st> they <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">live</st><p class=\"poetry\">and leave the <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">old</st> reliable <st data-num=\"07635\" class=\"\">path</st> of their fathers.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They have left them to <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">walk</st> in <st data-num=\"05410\" class=\"\">bypaths</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">in <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">roads</st> that are <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05549\" class=\"\">smooth and level</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">So their <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> will <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">become</st> an <st data-num=\"08047\" class=\"\">object of horror</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">People will <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">forever</st> <st data-num=\"08292\" class=\"\">hiss out</st> their <st data-num=\"08292\" class=\"\">scorn</st> over it.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> who <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">pass</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">that way</st> will <st data-num=\"08074\" class=\"\">be filled with horror</st><p class=\"poetry\">and will <st data-num=\"05110\" class=\"\">shake</st> their <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">heads</st> <st data-num=\"05110\" class=\"\">in derision</st>.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"06327\" class=\"\">scatter</st> them <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> their <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st><p class=\"poetry\">like dust blowing in front of a burning <st data-num=\"06921\" class=\"\">east</st> <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">wind</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will turn my <st data-num=\"06203\" class=\"\">back</st> on them and <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">look</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">favorably</st> on them<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">when</st> <st data-num=\"0343\" class=\"\">disaster</st> strikes them.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then some people<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">Come on</st>! Let us <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">consider</st> <st data-num=\"04284\" class=\"\">how to deal</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">with</st> <st data-num=\"03414\" class=\"\">Jeremiah</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> There will still <st data-num=\"03808 06\">be</st> <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">to instruct</st> us, <st data-num=\"02450\" class=\"\">wise men</st> to give us <st data-num=\"06098\" class=\"\">advice</st>, and <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophets</st> to declare God\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">word</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">Come on</st>! Let\u2019s <st data-num=\"03956\" class=\"\">bring charges</st> against him and <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">get rid of</st> him!<n id=\"4\" /> Then we will <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> need to <st data-num=\"07181\" class=\"\">pay attention</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">anything</st> he <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">says</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then I said,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"07181\" class=\"\">pay attention</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">Listen to</st> <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">what</st> my <st data-num=\"03401\" class=\"\">enemies</st> are <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">saying</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Should <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">good</st> be <st data-num=\"07999\" class=\"\">paid back</st> <st data-num=\"08478\" class=\"\">with</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil</st>?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Yet</st> they are virtually <st data-num=\"03738\" class=\"\">digging</st> a <st data-num=\"07745\" class=\"\">pit</st> to kill <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">me</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Just <st data-num=\"02142\" class=\"\">remember</st> how I <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">stood</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> you<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01696 02896\">pleading</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> their <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">behalf</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">to <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">keep</st> you <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">from venting</st> your <st data-num=\"02534\" class=\"\">anger</st> on <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">them</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">So</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">let</st> their <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">children</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">die</st> of <st data-num=\"07458\" class=\"\">starvation</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Let them be <st data-num=\"05064\" class=\"\">cut down</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">by</st> the <st data-num=\"03027 02719\">sword</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Let their <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wives</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">lose</st> their <st data-num=\"0490\" class=\"\">husbands</st> and <st data-num=\"07909\" class=\"\">children</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">Let</st> the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">older men</st> <st data-num=\"02026\" class=\"\">die</st> of <st data-num=\"04194\" class=\"\">disease</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"0970\" class=\"\">younger men</st> <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">die</st> by the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st> in <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">battle</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Let <st data-num=\"02201\" class=\"\">cries of terror</st> be <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> in their <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">houses</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">when</st> you <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">send</st> <st data-num=\"01416\" class=\"\">bands of raiders</st> <st data-num=\"06597\" class=\"\">unexpectedly</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to plunder</st> them.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> they have virtually <st data-num=\"03738\" class=\"\">dug</st> a <st data-num=\"07882\" class=\"\">pit</st> to <st data-num=\"03920\" class=\"\">capture</st> me<p class=\"poetry\">and have <st data-num=\"02934\" class=\"\">hidden</st> <st data-num=\"06341\" class=\"\">traps</st> for me to <st data-num=\"07272\" class=\"\">step</st> into.</p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "18",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">But <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st>, <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> their <st data-num=\"06098\" class=\"\">plots</st> <st data-num=\"05921 04194\">to kill</st> me.<p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03722 05921\">pardon</st> their <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">crimes</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">ignore</st> their <st data-num=\"02403\" class=\"\">sins</st> as though you had <st data-num=\"04229\" class=\"\">erased</st> them.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Let them <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"03782\" class=\"\">brought down in defeat</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> you.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">Deal</st> with them <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">while</st> you are still <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">angry</st>!\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  }
]